import pyautogui
import time

try:
    # Press Win key to open Start menu
    pyautogui.press('win')
    time.sleep(0.5)
    # Type 'notepad' to search
    pyautogui.write('notepad', interval=0.05)
    time.sleep(0.5)
    # Press Enter to launch
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(1)
    print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
except Exception as e:
    print("FAILED:", str(e))
